title: ESL Puzzle Game -- CHALLENGE MODE アダムのパズルゲーム

Message.message: Stage 11: push the middle red down and then back up.
Stage 12: you can only pull the gray blocks.
Stage 14: the gray will move up and down
Stage 15: Make 5 red in a row to win.  Blues first.
Stage 19: you must move and then replace the blue block to move the others.
Stage 20: don't close doors until you have to
